{
	"info": {
		"name": "Amrutam Telemedicine API",
		"description": "Complete end-to-end workflow collection for the Amrutam Telemedicine backend.\n\n## Workflow\n\n1. Health Checks\n2. Register users (patient, doctor, admin)\n3. Login as each role\n4. Patient: view/update profile\n5. Doctor: create profile & availability slots\n6. Public: search doctors\n7. Patient: book appointment → make payment\n8. Doctor: start & complete consultation\n9. Doctor: create prescription\n10. Patient: view consultations & prescriptions\n11. Admin: analytics & audit logs\n12. Authorization enforcement tests\n\n## Variables\n\nSet `base_url` to your Render deployment URL (e.g. `https://amrutam-telemedicine.onrender.com`) or `http://localhost:8000` for local testing.\n\n> Use **Run Collection** with the workflow order above for a fully automated end-to-end test.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "opencode"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "base_url",
			"value": "https://amrutam-telemedicine.onrender.com",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "patient_token",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "doctor_token",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "admin_token",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "patient_email",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "doctor_email",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "admin_email",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "doctor_id",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "slot_id",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "consultation_id",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
